Craig,

My rather hacked-over version of bind does recursion, as I
did not have a handy local server that would do recursion. I have
thus not run into this sort of problem. THere, of course, is
some inneficiency when you ask for x, get it as a name server,
and then ask x where x is. At least I get an answer, eventually.
